{"tid":2060261,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲想去日本轉生做Data Scientist","createTime":"2020-06-11T13:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T04:50:56.000Z","uid":54029,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d636798bc01f206be8009e4e9c01664ba1f5e544","tid":2060261,"uid":54029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫朋友宣傳下Data Science課程，要有日文大約N2程度，因為教學語言係日文。完成左3個月密集式課程後，就會幫你介紹日本既IT工作。如果成功係日本公司就職，可以退番學費。AI Academy本身有同FINDJAPANJOB合作，可以直接為有IT底既巴絲介紹日本既IT工。睇下各位巴絲有冇興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ai-academy.org/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fai-academy.org%2Fhk%2F&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0j%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=65eed692\" target=\"_blank\">https://ai-academy.org/hk/</a>"},{"pid":"10ecb7ff40319cbc60695e6f66e6d3617c08b582","tid":2060261,"uid":16061,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:46:37.000Z","msg":"搵錢要比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c34bcf1016b84be63c801094952c5abd73ef36","tid":2060261,"uid":48379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:48:20.000Z","msg":"日本唔知點解請好多海外IT"},{"pid":"1f3e08f48b7a1fc7ab87e8bbf05de07af0c288b3","tid":2060261,"uid":56624,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"日本返工已經係去做奴隸，返IT工真係等於自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5628f5ff5e3ab24cfee302569d031c312af0ce58","tid":2060261,"uid":341508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"學費人工前景如何？"},{"pid":"8634243689ece801bed039b8214df67230d0d073","tid":2060261,"uid":138809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020